title: Mario Kart Arcade GP + GP2 + 100% StateSaves + Tutorial Updated
description:
This is everything needed to play Mario Kart Arcade GP+GP2 on Dolphin Triforce on 32 

bit and 64 bit. It is completely updated with a step by step tutorial, screenshots, 

Statesave folders with the game 100% complete and one with 150cc Special started. No 

password on the 7z. Only reason why it is a 7z is so if someone makes a mistake 

copying files they can replace them easily. No where else can you find a complete 

version like this! HAVE FUN!
